<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夏天到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的菜园真好。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今年我们有很多蔬菜！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，胡萝卜长出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>豆子和草莓也长出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉米和西红柿也开始生长了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>全家人每天都到菜园里去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天晚上，他们都吃沙拉和其他蔬菜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们冷藏了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，菜园里还是有很多蔬菜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌去菜园。”哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“菜园有很多事情要做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！”妈妈说，“这些蔬菜真好吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菜园里的菜不停地生长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要怎么处理这些食物呢？”奥利弗问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道！”艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她告诉了大家她的想法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们做了个牌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着：“卖蔬菜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>挑你想吃的东西！付你能付的钱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把牌子立在外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，人们就看到了这个牌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多人来到菜园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们摘了豆子和玉米。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也摘了西红柿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把钱放在桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么用这笔钱？”奥利弗问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去买一张吊床吧。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去看棒球比赛吧。”哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道拿钱干什么了。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干什么？”大家问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她笑了。“买明年的种子！”</Text>
